Looking for a Chevrolet Equinox near Washington?

The Chevrolet Equinox offers the choice of three turbocharged power plants, as well as a traditional 6-speed automatic tranny mated to the base engine. Depending on your location, driving needs and habits, the Equinox offers a turbo targeting the task. With the largest selection of cars from dealers and private sellers, Autotrader can help find the perfect Equinox for you.

Autotrader has 4,685 Chevrolet Equinoxs for sale near Washington, DC, including a Certified 2015 Chevrolet Equinox FWD LS, a Used 2011 Chevrolet Equinox 2WD LT w/ 1LT, and a Used 2011 Chevrolet Equinox AWD LT.
